headline: VC Firm Eclipse Hires Investor Known for Rivian Bet
summary: Venture capital firm Eclipse has hired longtime T. Rowe Price investor Joe Fath as a partner and head of growth. Fath, known for his bets on companies including Tesla and Rivian, explains what he will bring to Eclipse, a firm focused on startups in physical industries, on "Bloomberg Tech."
